1
00:00:01,350 --> 00:00:02,990
《哥谭》前情提要
Previously on Gotham...

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,420
这位是雷吉纳德・佩恩
This is, Reginald Payne.

3
00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:05,560
我们是老战友  少爷
We served together, sir.

4
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:07,370
请安心在这里待几天吧
Please, feel free to stay with us a few days.

5
00:00:07,370 --> 00:00:09,000
你在偷我们的东西
You're stealing from us?

6
00:00:13,210 --> 00:00:14,090
阿诺德・弗拉斯
Arnold Flass.

7
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:16,510
你因杀害利昂・温克勒被捕了
You're under arrest for the murder of Leon Winkler.

8
00:00:16,510 --> 00:00:18,510
内务处说他是自杀
I.A. ruled it a suicide.

9
00:00:18,510 --> 00:00:20,020
阿诺德・弗拉斯  你被捕了
Arnold Flass, you're under arrest.

10
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,340
我有人罩着
I'm protected.

11
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:24,810
那么  惹事的就是你吗
So... you're the one causing all of the fuss.

12
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:27,940
你休想从我身上拿走任何东西
You will take nothing from me.

13
00:00:27,940 --> 00:00:29,040
是吗
Really?

14
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:33,430
不
No!

15
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:35,840
他没什么切实证据
He has nothing concrete.

16
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:38,590
现在是对那孩子采取行动的最佳时机
Now's the time to make a move on the kid.

17
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:49,480
食堂选择不多
Slim pickings at the food court.

18
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:52,170
-给你买了百吉饼  -谢谢
- Brought you a bagel. - Thanks.

19
00:00:52,170 --> 00:00:53,730
没给伤患买吗
Nothing for the invalid?

20
00:00:54,110 --> 00:00:56,990
抱歉  只能吃医院的食物
Sorry. Hospital food only.

21
00:00:57,090 --> 00:00:59,050
-医生嘱咐  感觉怎样  -还好
- Doctor's orders. How you feeling? - All right.

22
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:01,450
被刺伤了点
Had a slight... puncture.

23
00:01:01,450 --> 00:01:02,550
有点漏
Leaked a bit.

24
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:04,650
昨晚的事你估计都记不清了
So I know last night must be kind of a blur,

25
00:01:04,650 --> 00:01:07,330
但你知道是谁干的吗
but do you have any idea who did this?

26
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:07,900
是...
It-it was...

27
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,450
当时很黑  非常黑
It was dark. It was very dark.

28
00:01:09,450 --> 00:01:10,390
看到了
Saw a...

29
00:01:11,050 --> 00:01:12,560
一道黑影  然后...
shadow and...

30
00:01:13,590 --> 00:01:15,950
我的恩人布鲁斯少爷就站在我身边了
my savior Master Bruce was leaning over me.

31
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:17,800
你看到那人的长相了吗
Did you get a look at the guy?

32
00:01:18,700 --> 00:01:19,410
没有
No.

33
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:25,040
抱歉  警监不停打电话
Sorry. My captain keeps calling.

34
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,680
没事的  警探
It's fine, Detective.

35
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,990
-去吧  -没事  我可以留下
- Just-just go. - No, I can stay.

36
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,430
我真的很感谢你陪着布鲁斯少爷
I really appreciate you sitting with Master Bruce,

37
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:33,880
但如你所见  我都没事了
but as you can see, I'm completely fine.

38
00:01:34,790 --> 00:01:35,590
走吧
Go.

39
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:39,110
好  我尽量待会儿来看你们
All right. I'll try and stop by later.

40
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,240
再次谢谢你能来  警探
Thank you again for coming, Detective.

41
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,340
为什么不告诉他实情
Why not tell him the truth?

42
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:55,550
信不信由你  布鲁斯少爷  雷吉是我朋友
Well, believe it or not, Master Bruce, Reggie's a mate,

43
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:57,830
你不能让警察去抓朋友啊
and you don't set coppers on your mates, do you?

44
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,930
但他差点杀了你
But he nearly killed you.

45
00:01:58,930 --> 00:02:00,600
我跟那混球一起当过兵
I served with that bastard.

46
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:02,930
要有人去找他  也得是我
Anyone sorts him out, it's me-- nobody else.

47
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,070
否则不义气
It wouldn't be right.

48
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,430
他为什么要捅你
Why would he stab you?

49
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:08,010
这是个好问题
That's a bloody good question.

50
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:09,170
还是个
And one...

51
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:12,370
我想弄明白的问题
I mean to find out.

52
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:20,400
那疯子一天不抓回来
'Cause longer that bloody lunatic's out on the loose...

53
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:24,480
想找到他就越难
...the harder it's gonna be to find him.

54
00:02:24,650 --> 00:02:25,550
你去...
Now, you just...

55
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:29,340
回床上去  阿尔弗雷德
G-get back in bed, Alfred.

56
00:02:29,780 --> 00:02:30,730
把袍子给我
Just pass me my robe.

57
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:32,280
回床上去
Get back in bed!

58
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,000
这是命令
That's an order.

59
00:02:51,940 --> 00:02:52,810
你醒了
You're awake.

60
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,550
好极了
Wonderful.

61
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:57,720
我这是...
How long have I been...

62
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,720
睡了多久吗
Asleep?

63
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,440
就从昨晚到现在
Just since last night.

64
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,080
感觉如何
How do you feel?

65
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:05,490
头疼欲裂
My head hurts.

66
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:06,610
预料之中
To be expected.

67
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:07,810
让我看看
May I?

68
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:12,440
你是谁
Who are you?

69
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:15,220
弗兰西斯・杜马赫医生
Dr. Francis Dulmacher.

70
00:03:15,650 --> 00:03:17,420
这里的创建者
Founder of this facility.

71
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:19,240
很荣幸
A pleasure.

72
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:24,170
我为见你可是费尽心思啊  医生
I've gone to great lengths to meet you, Doctor.

73
00:03:24,170 --> 00:03:26,040
的确如此
Indeed you have.

74
00:03:27,170 --> 00:03:29,590
我得说  你们的体质令人赞叹
I must say you have a remarkable constitution.

75
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:32,330
真希望我所有病人都这样
I wish I could say the same of all my patients.

76
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:34,560
我现在是病人了吗
So I'm a patient now?

77
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:35,830
不再是囚犯了吗
No longer a prisoner?

78
00:03:35,830 --> 00:03:38,080
我说实话  我不知道你该算什么
I confess I don't know what you are.

79
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,010
你控制了地下室
You seize control of the basement,

80
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,730
绑架了我的一名守卫
take one of my guards hostage,

81
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:47,160
然后把自己的眼睛挖出来了
then scoop out your own eye.

82
00:03:47,490 --> 00:03:49,170
我该拿你怎么办
What am I to do with you?

83
00:03:49,410 --> 00:03:52,590
很简单  让我当你的左右手
Simple. Make me your right hand.

84
00:03:53,990 --> 00:03:56,430
很高兴你还会开玩笑
I'm glad to see you've retained your sense of humor.

85
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,500
我没开玩笑
I'm not joking.

86
00:03:58,970 --> 00:04:00,220
过去十年里
For the past ten years,

87
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:03,440
我一直都是卡麦・法尔科内的得力手下
I've been Carmine Falcone's top lieutenant.

88
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,460
不好意思  没听过那个名字
I'm afraid the name means nothing to me.

89
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:11,640
我被关进了地下牢房  又饿又孤独
I woke up hungry and alone in an underground cell.

90
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,890
不到一周  我就把这里闹得天翻地覆
In less than a week, I brought this place to a standstill.

91
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:17,060
你试过了与我为敌
Now, you've had me as your enemy.

92
00:04:18,110 --> 00:04:20,350
你难道不希望我跟你站一边吗
Wouldn't you rather have me as your friend?

93
00:04:20,350 --> 00:04:21,530
真有活力
Such vim.

94
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,540
真有派头
Such... panache.

95
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,430
好极了
Bravo.

96
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:29,170
现在你该吃饭了
And now you should eat.

97
00:04:29,570 --> 00:04:31,230
我让护士送点食物进来
I'll have a nurse come in with some food.

98
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,590
咱们等会儿再聊
We'll talk more later.

99
00:04:33,570 --> 00:04:36,170
眼睛这东西挺难搞的
Tricky things, eyes.

100
00:04:36,170 --> 00:04:38,880
目前我们的存货少得可怜
Our stock is frightfully low at the moment.

101
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,840
很抱歉了
Oh, and apologies.

102
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:43,060
我们没找到与你原来颜色相同的
We couldn't match your original color.

103
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:46,270
咱们等下再聊
We'll talk soon.

