哥谭
第一季  第十八集

110
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:23,300
{\an8}缉毒组警探无罪释放  谋杀罪名撤销

111
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,070
这不可能
This can't be true.

112
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,070
我正在给地检官准备案子
I was prepping the case for the D.A.

113
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,820
结果今天早上就听到了消息
when word came down this morning.

114
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,830
显然媒体昨晚就知道了
Press got it last night, of course.

115
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:30,690
我们手上有谋杀凶器
We had the murder weapon.

116
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:32,420
上边有弗拉斯的指纹
With Flass's prints.

117
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:33,260
这不可能
There's no way.

118
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:35,080
显然  辩方找来了一位证人
Apparently, the defense dug up a witness,

119
00:05:35,090 --> 00:05:36,750
洗清了弗拉斯的罪名
cleared Flass of all charges.

120
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,590
-什么证人  -不知道
- What witness? - No idea.

121
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:40,870
只有法官和首席律师知道
Only the judge and the lead attorneys were privy,

122
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:43,610
而我们可敬的地检官不肯说
and our honorable D.A. is staying mum.

123
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:44,450
那传唤呢
What about a subpoena?

124
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:45,980
我们没有足够的理由
We don't have sufficient grounds.

125
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,390
但是我四处打听了一下
But I did a little snooping around.

126
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,430
怎么样
And?

127
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:52,120
那位神秘证人是洛布局长提供的
The mystery witness was provided by Commissioner Loeb.

128
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,680
让我猜猜
Let me guess.

129
00:05:57,370 --> 00:05:59,530
洛布恢复了弗拉斯缉毒组组长的身份
Loeb's reinstating Flass as head of Narco.

130
00:05:59,530 --> 00:06:00,410
更糟
Worse.

131
00:06:00,570 --> 00:06:02,410
他宣布支持弗拉斯参加
He announced he's backing Flass for president

132
00:06:02,410 --> 00:06:04,800
即将到来的警察工会主席的竞选
of the policemen's union in the upcoming election.

133
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,080
所以你是说一个我们已知是毒贩子
So you're telling me a man we know is a drug dealer

134
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,160
和杀人凶手的人
and a murderer

135
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:11,020
将有可能在哥谭市警局出任要职
is gonna potentially hold a major position in the GCPD?

136
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:12,980
洛布显然是在示威
Clearly, Loeb's sending a message.

137
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,630
这不可容忍
This is not gonna stand.

138
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:16,600
我和你一样失望  吉姆
Look, I'm just as upset about this as you are, Jim,

139
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,060
但他是局长
but it's the commissioner.

140
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:19,700
所以情况更糟了
Which is what makes it worse.

141
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,420
吉姆  吉姆
Jim! Jim!

142
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,320
吉姆
Jimbo.

143
00:06:32,030 --> 00:06:33,540
你听到好消息了吗
You heard the good news?

144
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:38,100
伙计们正准备在奥唐丽餐厅给我开场回归宴
Hey, the boys are throwing me a welcome back down at O'Donnelys.

145
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,190
不知道你想不想来看看
Figure you want to stop by.

146
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:43,130
支持一下你的准新主席
Show support for your soon-to-be new president.

147
00:06:43,130 --> 00:06:45,080
我看你还是别急着庆祝
I wouldn't celebrate just yet.

148
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,550
你就是学不乖
You just don't learn.

149
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:50,000
还想搞掉我呢
Still want to take me down.

150
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:52,740
我就像是凤凰
I'm like the phoenix.

151
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,700
我会浴火重生
I'll just rise

152
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:58,970
一次  一次  又一次
again and again and again.

153
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,040
戈登警探
Ah, Detective Gordon.

154
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:10,380
我就预感你会来找我
I had a presentiment I might be seeing you.

155
00:07:10,810 --> 00:07:12,550
阿诺德・弗拉斯是个杀人犯
Arnold Flass is a murderer.

156
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,010
他应该待在监狱里
He belongs in jail.

157
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:16,120
弗拉斯警探依法无罪释放
Detective Flass was legally exonerated.

158
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,850
法官听取了证词  案件结束了
The judge heard testimony. The case is closed.

159
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:24,250
你是动用关系安排他获释
You used your connections to orchestrate his release.

160
00:07:25,470 --> 00:07:26,970
你玷污了体制
You perverted the system.

161
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:30,520
暴躁和天真是个坏组合
Petulance and naiveté are a bad combination.

162
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,080
输了就要认命
Know when you're beaten.

163
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:36,210
弗拉斯的调查我介入很深
I was knee-deep in the Flass investigation.

164
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:38,330
没有人能有足够的可信度
There is no one with enough credibility

165
00:07:38,330 --> 00:07:39,810
来推翻我们的证据
to trump our evidence.

166
00:07:42,130 --> 00:07:44,360
我很喜欢不可动摇的信念
I do enjoy when unwavering certainty

167
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,880
被真相击碎的时刻
is undermined by the truth.

168
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,050
看着镜头  说出你的名字
Look into the camera, state your name

169
00:07:51,050 --> 00:07:52,110
还有为什么会在这里
and why you're here.

170
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:54,150
我是哈维・布洛克警探
My name is Detective Harvey Bullock,

171
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:56,340
我使用了假证据指证了
and I presented false evidence against

172
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:59,930
我哥谭市警局同事  阿诺德・弗拉斯警探
my fellow GCPD detective, Arnold Flass.

173
00:08:09,210 --> 00:08:10,440
你在这儿啊
Hey, there you are.

174
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:13,100
老兄  我感觉就像是昨晚有一群牛
Aw, dude. Feel like a herd of cattle had a dance party

175
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,030
在脑子里开了一场舞会
in my head last night.

176
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:14,870
有什么事吗
What's up?

177
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:17,420
你为什么要撒谎保弗拉斯
Why the hell would you lie to exonerate Flass?

178
00:08:19,690 --> 00:08:21,420
别否认  我都看到录像带了
Don't deny it. I saw the tape.

179
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:23,090
我也没打算否认
I'm not denying anything.

180
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,520
我那是迫不得已
I did what I had to do.

181
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:29,280
如果我不按洛布说的做  早就被开除了
If I didn't do what Loeb told me to do, I would've lost my job.

182
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,710
说不定都进监狱了
Probably gone to prison.

183
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:33,680
他有你什么把柄
